Class EventHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.goodees.ese.core.EventHeader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Event

    public class EventHeader
extends Object
implements Event
    Default implementation of required event fields. This may serve either as base class for actual event implementations, and also for event factories to fill common data fields by just providing reference to the entity.
